09/21/82  send_mail request:  subject, sj

Syntax:  sj {STRs}


Syntax as an active request:  [sj]


Function:  changes the subject of the message or prints the current
subject.  As an active request, it returns the current subject as a
single, quoted string.


Arguments:
STRs
   specifies the new subject of the message.  If no STRs are given, the
   current subject will be printed.
